Question.Subject: Is there a world like Club Cooee for English?
Question.Content: Well I downloaded Club Cooee and thought it was pretty cool, I love the way its on your desktop and you can drag it around. The only problem is that all the people on it are German. Is there a world like this that isn't German? Thanks (:
Question.ChosenAnswer:
Hey,
Yes there is an English version for it, get it here http://www.clubcooee.com/ make sure top right of the web page that you select English as your language then download.
Hope that helps
